spec_data.Name: texlive-marginnote
spec_data.Description:
This package provides the command \marginnote that may be used
instead of \marginpar at almost every place where \marginpar
cannot be used, e.g., inside floats, footnotes, or in frames
made with the framed package.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 08:12:09 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Notes in the margin, even where \marginpar fails
